data.text:
I was just having a little look through YouTube when I found the amazing vocals of Caroline Jones, with her brand new song “Rise (Sing It Loud)”!

I will admit this is the first time I have heard the vocals of Caroline Jones, and all I am asking myself is why has it taken me this long to hear them? Her vocals are just incredibly beautiful & pure, and suits the tone of the song really well.

The lyrics of the song are very catchy and showcase Caroline’s incredible songwritting skills.

This song has quickly become one of my favourites of 2017 so far.

You can check out the official video below!
